{"tid":1263073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"8前問責官聯署 促設獨立調查","createTime":"2019-06-28T03:48:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T07:28:43.000Z","uid":212626,"like":54,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0f3cf46c91b7389d36809225892b9d1e9555a3a0","tid":1263073,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T03:48:12.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】8名前問責官員聯署，促請政府設立由資深大法官主持的<span style=\"color: red;\">法定獨立調查委員會</span>，調查6月12日警民衝突成因和過程；在委員會完成調查及提出建議前，暫緩所有與6．12及其後引發的衝突中，針對示威者及警務人員的任何檢控。聲明強調，調查是為和解，建議特首在調查結果的基礎上，<span style=\"color: red;\">考慮按《基本法》酌情頒布不同程度的特赦</span>。<br />\n<br />\n籲特首酌情特赦 暫緩檢控<br />\n另外，監警會確認主席梁定邦向監警會成員建議，會方應<span style=\"color: red;\">主動審視近期的大型公眾活動</span>，以履行法定職能，現時正就建議作內部討論，監警會<span style=\"color: red;\">短期內會交代未來計劃</span>。<br />\n<br />\n修訂《逃犯條例》引發本月12日在立法會外一帶發生警民衝突，及後示威者發動包圍警察總部。<span style=\"color: green;\">勞福局前局長蕭偉強、運房局前副局長邱誠武、商經局前副局長梁敬國、食衛局前政治助理陳智遠、勞福局前政助莫宜端、環境局前政助蔡少綿及兩任財政司長前政助羅永聰和葉根銓聯署</span>，指民眾對警方不滿未有減退，警方成為磨心，事態發展令人痛心，社會又再處於分化撕裂狀態，呼籲特首林鄭月娥以實際行動促進社會各方和解，前提是和解必須建基於客觀事實和真相。<br />\n<br />\n聯署指出，相關調查會提出改善建議，有助政府及執法機關日後與公民社會建立新互動關係，妥善應對將來大型社會運動和示威行動。<br />\n<br />\n（反修例風暴）<br />\n<br />\nSource：明報<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e8%a6%81%e8%81%9e/article/20190628/s00001/1561659575602\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a6%2581%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190628%2Fs00001%2F1561659575602&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2FewiyebWXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=5f5b6210\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a6%2581%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190628%2Fs00001%2F1561659575602&h=12010ed4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e8%a6%81%e8%81%9e/article/20190628/s00001/1561659575602</a>"},{"pid":"fb063c519622197f221cf1b2a7f3f65720908351","tid":1263073,"uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T03:50:18.000Z","msg":"相關報導：<br />\n32名前高官議員聯署促撤回修例 調查612金鐘衝突<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1252803/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1252803/page/2</a><br />\n突發！22名前高官和資深立法會議員聯署聲明<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1221122/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1221122/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"79038f87d87165a62cb9190255a321f3854cb2e5","tid":1263073,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T03:54:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0df92f571beb81e2634639b242fbd275672a852e","tid":1263073,"uid":212626,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T03:58:57.000Z","msg":"唔知到最後會有幾多個前高官/立會議員聯署反修例<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d112fb660ffd627c1d7765686fe28b9310096a2","tid":1263073,"uid":160257,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T03:59:13.000Z","msg":"市民抗爭就追究到底，犬方濫權就包庇到底，玩晒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又話好人好者唔怕逃犯條例<br />\n咁好人好者點解怕獨立調查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac41381fab300545ba6950c441df756dd91330f","tid":1263073,"uid":253826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T04:02:03.000Z","msg":"市民聲音唔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前高官都唔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n港共政府幾時俾天收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"688a1aaf0242346ac2f30b6c46bf950fba01e91f","tid":1263073,"uid":192052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ac41381fab300545ba6950c441df756dd913